    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1936-09-10T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1936-09-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="62"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d62">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">724.34119/614</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Paraguay</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Howard</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 258</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Asunción</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-09-10">September 10,
                            1936</date>.<lb/>[Received September 25.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to refer to the fund of
                    2,400,000 Argentine pesos paid by the Bolivian Government to the Paraguayan
                    Government which is now on deposit in Buenos Aires, having been turned over to
                    that latter Government in connection with the termination of the repatriation of
                    prisoners, and to inform the Department that in a conversation with Dr.
                    Stefanich, the Minister for Foreign Affairs, this morning, he stated that this
                    sum would be placed in the Banco de la Republica to be used for conversion and
                    for stabilizing the Paraguayan paper peso.</p>
                <p>Respectfully yours,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Findley Howard</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
